<template>
  <sidebar-layout-vue>
    <v-container class="fill-height flex-column" fluid>
        <v-card :width="800"
          height="100%"
          class="mx-auto"
          outilined
          elevation="3">
          <v-container>
            <v-row dense>
              <v-col cols="12">
                <v-toolbar flat
                        rounded
                        dense
                        class="blue-grey lighten-4">
                  <v-toolbar-title class="font-weight-medium">{{title}}</v-toolbar-title>
                </v-toolbar>
              </v-col>
              <v-col cols="12">
                  <v-text-field :label="searchlabel">

                  </v-text-field>
              </v-col>
            </v-row>
          </v-container>
        </v-card>
    </v-container>
  </sidebar-layout-vue>
</template>

<script>
import SidebarLayoutVue from "@/layouts/SidebarLayout.vue";
import { stringify } from "json5";

export default {
  name:"users",
  components: {
    SidebarLayoutVue
  },
  data() {
    return {
      title: "Cadastro de Usuários",
      searchlabel:"Pesquisar"
    }
  },
}
</script>
